Icyayi mu [[Rwanda]] kizwi cyane ku [[isi]] kubera kwinjiza no kumurika Icyayi cyo mu misozi yo mu [[Rwanda]] gitanga [[icyayi]] cyiza mu [[Rwanda]] ushora imari mu gutunganya [[icyayi]], gukurikirana impuguke no kuyobora mu gutanga umusaruro.  

== Rwanda Mountain Tea ==
Guhera mu 2006, '''Rwanda Mountain Tea Ltd''' yabaye umushoramari wigenga w’abasangwabutaka mu nganda z’icyayi n’imirima, agura imigabane myinshi mu mitungo myinshi yahoze ari iya leta, harimo , Nyabihu na Rubyaa (mu [[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|burengerazuba]] no mu [[Intara y’Amajyaruguru y’u Rwanda|majyaruguru]]), [[Icyayi cya Kitabi|Kitabi]] (mu [[Intara y'amajyepfo|majyepfo]]),<ref>https://www.igihe.com/ubukungu/ubucuruzi/article/icyayi-cya-kitabi-n-icya-gisovu-byaciye-agahigo-ku-isoko-muri-kenya?fbclid=IwAR0vrg71iNhFPv5HOYi7DWSxf-1-PcWyDKgtz0i3nQ9UofRTGXLdZT6ZuGU</ref> na Gisakura na Mata (mu [[Intara y'amajyepfo|majyepfo]] y'[[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|iburengerazuba]]) .

== Kwagura Ibikorwa ==
Byongeye kandi, muri gahunda yo kwagura, '''Rwanda Mountain Tea Ltd''' yashoye gushinga uruganda rw'[[icyayi]] ahitwa [[Akarere ka Rutsiro|Rutsiro]] ([[Intara y'Uburengerazuba|mu intara y'burengerazuba]]), kabuhariwe mu gukora CTC yumukara, [[icyayi]] cyumukara nicyatsi kibisi Ikindi cyiyongereyeho ni uruganda rwicyayi rwa Gatare mu karere ka [[Akarere ka Nyamasheke|Nyamasheke]] ruteganijwe gukoreshwa mbere yuyu mwaka.<ref>https://maps.prodafrica.com/places/rwanda/kigali-city/kigali/tea-producer/rwanda-mountain-tea-ltd/</ref>

== Ishoramari ==
Ishoramari rya '''Rwanda Mountain Tea Ltd''' mu ishoramari ry’[[icyayi]] rigamije kuzamura umusaruro w’[[icyayi]] binyuze mu buhinzi bwiza no kubona no kwagura imirima y’icyayi mu gihugu hose. Umuzenguruko warangiye mu kuzamura no kubaka inganda z'[[icyayi]] zigezweho no gushyiraho uruganda rwicyayi ruvanga nogupakira [[icyayi]] kugirango gikemure abakoresha [[icyayi]] mu [[Rwanda]] kandi buhoro buhoro mukarere ndetse no mubindi bice bya [[Afurika|Afrika]].  '''Rwanda Mountain Tea Ltd''' izwi kwisi yose kubera gukora [[icyayi]] cyiza cya CTC cyiza ku [[isi]], kandi yatsindiye ibihembo bitandukanye by'[[icyayi]] ku [[isi]].<ref>https://www.minagri.gov.rw/index.php?id=544&tx_kesearch_pi1%5Bsword%5D=icyayi&tx_kesearch_pi1%5Bpage%5D=1&tx_kesearch_pi1%5BresetFilters%5D=0&tx_kesearch_pi1%5BsortByField%5D=&tx_kesearch_pi1%5BsortByDir%5D=</ref>

=== Amashanyarazi ===
Usibye gukora no gucuruza icyayi, '''Rwanda Mountain Tea Ltd''' numushoramari wigenga mu kongera ingufu. Kugeza ubu igomba gushyiraho inganda z'amashanyarazi 2 y'umugezi wa Giciye itanga MW 8 kuri gride y'[[igihugu]].Ari mubikorwa byo kubaka urundi r'uganda kumugezi umwe gifite ubushobozi bwa MW 7.2. Mu bindi bikorwa bifitanye isano, Rwanda Mountain Tea Ltd yasinyanye na leta yu [[Rwanda]] amasezerano y’inguzanyo ku nganda 2 zisanzwe zikoresha amashanyarazi kugira ngo zongere MW 4. Ibigo mu matsinda bivanga mu buryo bworoshye mu baturage bakoreramo, bigira uruhare mu kubaka [[Ishuri|amashuri]], ibigo ndzerabuzima, imihanda igaburira, n’amazu ku bakene cyane.  Bagira uruhare kandi muri gahunda y'[[igihugu]] yinka imwe kumuryango ukennye buri mwaka baha amatungo imiryango itishoboye. <ref>https://maps.prodafrica.com/places/rwanda/kigali-city/kigali/tea-producer/rwanda-mountain-tea-ltd/</ref>

=== Ibindi ===
'''Rwanda Mountain Tea Ltd''' itanga imirimo irenga 25.000 kubaturage bo mucyaro usibye kugura ibabi ryatsi kubuhinzi-borozi, bityo bagatanga isoko ryumwaka wose kubicuruzwa byabo. Isosiyete ihuza neza n’abaturage aho ikorera, igira uruhare mu iterambere ry’imibereho n’ubukungu by’abaturage binyuze muri;  kubaka amashuri, ibigo nderabuzima, umuhanda ugaburira, amazu kubakene cyane no kuzana amazi meza kubaturage.<ref>https://www.minagri.gov.rw/index.php?id=544&tx_kesearch_pi1%5Bsword%5D=icyayi&tx_kesearch_pi1%5Bpage%5D=1&tx_kesearch_pi1%5BresetFilters%5D=0&tx_kesearch_pi1%5BsortByField%5D=&tx_kesearch_pi1%5BsortByDir%5D=</ref>

Hanyuma, '''Rwanda Mountain Tea Ltd''' ni umusoreshwa munini kandi igashora inyungu mu [[Igihugu|gihugu]], bityo ikagira uruhare mu iterambere ry’u [[Rwanda]].<ref>https://maps.prodafrica.com/places/rwanda/kigali-city/kigali/tea-producer/rwanda-mountain-tea-ltd/</ref>

